==Translingual==
===Symbol===
'''J'''

#(''metrology'') The symbol for [[joule]], the [[unit]] of [[work]] or [[energy]] in the [[International System of Units]]

----
==English==
===Noun===
'''J''' or '''j'''

# The tenth letter of the [[Wiktionary:About Roman script|English alphabet]].
# (''slang'') A term for a [[marijuana]] cigarette ('joint').
#:''"I went outside to smoke myself a <i>'J'</i>" &mdash; [[w:Paul Simon (musician)|Paul Simon]], from the song "One Trick Pony."''

==={{abbreviation}}===
'''J'''

#[[journal|Journal]]
